high_descs: Turn and look around the room, now turn back and face the trash can
Take the toilet paper off of the holder
While holding the toilet paper look around the room first right and now left
Put the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet
Turn toward the sink and face the one on the end
Open the cupboard under the sink and remove an empty roll of toilet paper in side of it, now close the cupboard
While holding the empty roll turn left and take a few steps
Place the empty roll on the back of the toilet next to the full one
anns.task_desc: Get the toilet paper and the empty roll of toilet paper now place on the back of the toilet

high_descs: Take a step to the left, so you're lined up with the toilet paper.
Remove the toilet paper roll from the holder.
Turn left so  you're facing the tub, but still by the toilet.
Place the toilet paper on the lid to the toilet's tank at the end closest to the flush lever.
Turn to your right and face the leftmost sink.
Open the cupboard beneath the sink closest to the toilet and pick up the empty toilet paper roll from inside.
Turn left to move closer to the toilet while facing the tub again.
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the tank lid to the left of the other roll you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper rolls to the tank lid of the toilet.

high_descs: Stand in front of the roll of toilet on the left side of the sink.
Take the roll of toilet paper from the holder.
Turn right, take a step in that direction, then left.
Head towards the toilet on the left side of the sink.
Place the roll of toilet on the back of the toilet.
Turn around towards the sink then stand in front of it.
Open the left cabinet door underneath the sink, remove the cup in the cabinet, then close the door.
Turn back towards the toilet, place the cup on the left of the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Place a roll of toilet paper and a cup on the back of a toilet.
